---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Learn how we handle your personal data.">
  <section class="py-12 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting any personal information you share with us. This policy outlines the types of information we collect and how we use it.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-2">Information Collection</h2>
    <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">We may collect personal details such as your name, email address, and phone number when you fill out forms on our site. Supplying this information is voluntary, though it may be required to access certain services.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-2">Use of Information</h2>
    <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">We use the information you provide to respond to inquiries, process listings, and improve our services. We will not use your contact details for unsolicited marketing without your consent.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-2">Data Sharing</h2>
    <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">Severino Realty does not sell or rent personal information to third parties. We may share aggregated, non-identifiable data with partners to improve our services.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-2">Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-neutral-700">If you have any questions about this policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@severino.com" class="text-cta hover:text-accent">info@severino.com</a>.</p>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
